CM_ "Version:V1.3.0,Date:2025/8/29,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:向宇设变,Description:(DSM)1、新增报文PSM_0x5FB，报文中新增信号PSM_ZeroGravityUnfoldBtn，PSM_ZeroGravityFoldBtn，PSM_ZeroGravityFoldSt，PSM_SeatAngleMotPosn，均是PSM发，VIU1_CABIN收；
2、报文VIU_3A4中新增VIU_PsmZeroGravityFoldFunSet，VIU1_CABIN发，PSM收；
3、报文RDS_345中新增RDS_RLSecRowSeatHeatLvlSet，RDS_RLSecRowSeatVentLvlSet，RDS_RRSecRowSeatHeatLvlSet，RDS_RRSecRowSeatVentLvlSet，均是RDS发，VIU1_CABIN收；
4、新增报文VIU_347，报文中新增信号VIU_LRSM_HeatgSts，VIU_LRSM_VentnSts，VIU_RRSM_HeatgSts，VIU_RRSM_VentnSts，均是VIU1_CABIN发，RDS收；
5、新增DSM节点；;
Version:V2.0.0,Date:2025/9/23,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:高永建设变,Description:(DSM)1、报文PSM_0x5FB中新增PSM_ZeroGravityforbiddenReasonSt，PSM发，VIU1_CABIN收；
2、报文VIU_DSM_0x39A中新增VIU_DrvrSeatLegSupportMotPosnStepSet，VIU_DrvrSeatLegExtnMotPosnStepSet，VIU0_IP发，DSM收；;
Version:V2.0.0,Date:2025/9/26,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:高永建设变,Description:(DSM)1、DSM,PSM取消加热状态信号，涉及DSM,PSM,VIU0_IP,VIU1_CABIN；;
Version:V2.0.0,Date:2025/9/30,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:胡新安设变,Description:(DSM)1、DSM新增电机防夹，电流，hall周期等信号，涉及DSM,VIU0_IP；;
Version:V2.1.0,Date:2025/11/17,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:胡新安设变,Description:(DSM)1、删除涉及步进调节相关信号，涉及DSM,VIU0_IP；;
Version:V2.1.0,Date:2025/11/20,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:高永建需求,Description:(DSM)1、新增信号VIU_BackLiBriSet，涉及DSM,VIU0_IP；;
Version:V4.1.0,Date:2025/12/24,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:胡新安设变,Description:(DSM)1、报文VIU_DSM_0x393中新增设计预留信号VIU_DrvrSeatSLCUotPosnStepSet，VIU_DrvrSeatCushHeiMotPosnStepSet，VIU_DrvrSeatCushTiltMotPosnStepSet，VIU_DrvrSeatBackrestMotPosnStepSet，涉及DSM,VIU0_IP；;
Version:V4.1.0,Date:2026/1/10,Author:ranzhao,Review:,Approval:梁龙凯设变,Description:(DSM)1、新增DSM_CushTiltMotPosn，删除DSM_SeatAngleMotPosn,涉及DSM,VIU0_IP；
2、PSM_CushTiltMotPosn 信号值描述更新，删除信号PSM_SeatAngleMotPosn，涉及PSM,VIU1_CABIN；;
Version:V5.2.0,Date:2026/4/17,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:梁龙凯设变,Description:(DSM)1、报文VIU_DSM_0x39A中新增信号VIU_DrvrSeatStopAdjustCmd，VIU_DSM_0x39A_Checksum，VIU_DSM_0x39A_Counter，涉及DSM,VIU0_IP；;
Version:V5.2.0,Date:2026/4/20,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:胡新安设变,Description:(DSM)1、新增报文DSM_AP_DiffCurrent，PSM_AP_DiffCurrent，涉及DSM,PSM；;
 ";

